title: Rek sai, are you joking? This champ will be dominating the jungle for a LONG TIME
body:
HAH what a joke, this champ kit, i mean how can you release this champ while nerfing Warwick? this new champ shits all over pre nerf warwick in every way.

Welp gg l2p rek because  she will own the jungle for a long long time. Mobily , dmg , clear , cc, sustain.....got it all baby,

replies.body: Umm Warwick's changes are justifiable, since you can almost one-hit KO any enemies with stacked Devourer with just one ult.
She's the only one designed to fit into the new jungle. They haven't altered other champs to help them in the new jungle because they don't know what a huge wave of QoL changes will do to balance.
